Microsoft (R) Team Foundation Field Mapping Tool

Uploads or downloads the file that defines how fields are mapped between
Microsoft Office Project and Team Foundation Server. To use this tool, you
must be a member of either the Team Foundation Administrators group or the
Project Administrators group for the team project that you specify.
upload        Uploads the field mapping file for the team project that you
download      Downloads the field mapping file for the team project that you
